{
  "texts": [
    "It utilizes the propagation graph to represent various data elements such as source posts, source microblogs, forwarded microblogs, comments and users.",
    "Structural information is then extracted using GCN.",
    "The attention mechanism is employed to decrease the weight of inaccurate edges within the propagation graph.",
    "This reduction in weight helps to mitigate interference and enhance the accuracy of rumor detection. 3.",
    "The third module is the rumor prediction classification module."
  ]
}